# Telemetry Integration Guide

## Overview

This guide covers integrating the OmniSight telemetry SDK into your
{{ product_name | default("embedded device") }} firmware. The SDK captures
three event types — crash dumps, usage events, and performance metrics —
and delivers them to the ingestion backend with offline queuing, PII
redaction, and consent enforcement.

